data.description: Golf course frontage home located at one of Orlando's most sought-after communities near Lake Nona. This Mediterranean style two story home features 5 bedrooms and 4 bathrooms. As you walk into the elegant double front doors you will be welcomed by the spacious living room area that overlooks the fairway of hole #3. The formal dining room is spacious and great to gather family reunions and create special moments. Continuing, adjacent to the stairs, the kitchen and family room featuring granite counters, 42” cabinets, stainless steel appliances, a walk-in pantry, coffee/bar area, and elegant ceiling crown molding. Plantation shutters throughout the house to allow as much natural light as you need. With a 3 car, NEW Roof (installed March 2024), Energy efficient double panel windows, high ceilings with 8-foot doors throughout, and granite counters in all bathrooms, this home is move-in ready for your family.  The screened back porch will allow you to enjoy all year-round the nature view this unique house offers. Eagle Creek community has an European flair and offers spectacular amenities including a 4½ star Championship Golf Course, rated by Golf Digest, a two-story Golf Clubhouse with Pro Shop, Lounge and Restaurant, Family Recreation Clubhouse with Fitness Center and Gathering Room, Resort-Style Pool, Pool with splash pads and  Expansive Sundeck, Tennis Courts, Basketball Courts, Covered Playground and Multi-Purpose Ball Field, and more. Eagle Creek Elementary School in the community for convenience and top-rated middle and high school nearby. Minutes from Lake Nona Town Center, USTA, MCO airport, shopping stores, banks, and hospitals.   A Luxury living lifestyle awaits you in this home. Schedule your showing today!
